---
// No props needed
---
<div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8 my-8">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6 text-center">Before You Book Checklist</h2>

  <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-trust mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <strong>Confirm your main concern:</strong> Determine if you are seeking developmental guidance, behavior strategies, or a formal diagnosis (which requires local care).
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-trust mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <strong>Choose the type of support:</strong> Decide between a one-off consultation, an ongoing program, or school support.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-trust mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <strong>Review provider profile:</strong> Check the credentials and expertise of available providers.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-trust mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <strong>Check service boundaries:</strong> Ensure you understand what is included (education) and what is not (therapy/diagnosis) based on your location.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-trust mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
      <div>
        <strong>Understand privacy & emergency limits:</strong> Review our privacy policies and note that this platform is not for emergency care.
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
